  # Flock — Social Coordination Simplified

  Flock is a real-time social coordination app that replaces the broken group chat planning process with structured decision-making. Create a flock, invite friends, vote on venues, match budgets anonymously,
  and go.

  **Live app:** [flockcorp.com](https://flockcorp.com)

  ---

  ## The Problem

  Group chats turn into indecisive "idk what do you want to do" loops. Someone suggests somewhere expensive. Two people go silent because they can't afford it but won't say so. The plan dies. Everyone stays
  home.

  Flock fixes this with a structured coordination flow: **create → invite → RSVP → vote → match budgets → confirm → go.**

  ---

  ## Core Features

  ### Real-Time Coordination
  - Create flocks with time, date, and venue context
  - Invite friends and track RSVPs (going / maybe / declined)
  - Group venue voting with Google Places integration
  - Real-time messaging with typing indicators, emoji reactions, image sharing, and venue cards
  - Live location sharing within flocks

  ### Anonymous Budget Matching
  - Every member privately submits their max budget — no one sees individual answers
  - Server computes the group spending ceiling (minimum of all submissions)
  - Venues above the group budget are hidden automatically
  - 3-person minimum threshold protects anonymity
  - Individual submissions are deleted 24 hours after the flock completes

  ### Birdie — AI Assistant
  - Conversational AI assistant powered by Gemini 2.5 Flash with function calling
  - Searches venues, checks crowd levels, and coordinates plans through natural language
  - Understands Gen Z slang ("what's poppin", "the move", "lit", "dead")
  - Returns interactive venue cards with photos, crowd bars, ratings, and share actions
  - Expandable chat widget — compact floating bubble, mid-size panel, or fullscreen mode
  - 3D Spline robot avatar with head tracking

  ### AI Crowd Intelligence Engine
  - Autonomous engine that perceives real-time data from multiple sources — Google Places, OpenWeatherMap, and temporal patterns — reasons over them using a weighted multi-factor scoring algorithm, and
  generates crowd predictions, timing recommendations, and alternative venue suggestions
  - Scores venues 0–100 with confidence ratings based on data source availability
  - 12-hour hourly forecast, capacity estimates, wait times, best time to visit
  - Self-calibrating: user feedback after hangouts adjusts prediction weights over time, turning every completed flock into training data

  ### ML Crowd Forecasting (In Development)
  - XGBoost/Random Forest model trained on BestTime foot traffic data, weather signals, venue metadata, and user feedback
  - 6,000+ venues discovered across 7 cities with automated data collection pipeline
  - Event awareness via Ticketmaster API for nearby concert/sports impact on crowd levels
  - Designed to replace the rule-based engine with learned predictions

  ### Bill Splitting + Venmo Settlement
  - Post-hangout bill split with equal or custom amounts
  - Tip calculator (15% / 18% / 20% / custom)
  - Venmo deep-link settlement — one tap opens Venmo pre-filled with the correct amount and recipient
  - Ghost Mode pre-commitment — lock in your share before arriving to reduce flaking
  - No payment processing, no APIs, no transaction fees

  ### Social Layer
  - Friend system with QR code sharing and phone-based discovery
  - Direct messages with venue cards, voting, pinning, replies, and reactions
  - 24-hour expiring stories
  - User profiles with image upload

  ### Safety
  - Trusted emergency contacts management
  - One-tap SOS alert sends GPS location to all contacts via email (Resend)
  - Real-time location sharing within flocks and DMs

  ---

  ## Tech Stack

  | Layer | Technology |
  |-------|-----------|
  | Frontend | React 19 (Create React App) |
  | Backend | Node.js + Express |
  | Database | PostgreSQL |
  | Real-Time | Socket.io WebSockets |
  | Frontend Hosting | Vercel |
  | Backend Hosting | Railway |
  | Authentication | JWT (24h expiry, bcrypt password hashing) |
  | AI Assistant | Gemini 2.5 Flash-Lite (function calling) |
  | Venue Data | Google Places API (New) |
  | Weather Data | OpenWeatherMap API |
  | Crowd Data | BestTime API |
  | Event Data | Ticketmaster Discovery API |
  | Email | Resend (HTTP-based) |
  | 3D | Spline |
  | Font | Satoshi (Fontshare CDN) |

