  ## API Endpoints

  ### Authentication
  | Method | Route | Description |
  |--------|-------|-------------|
  | POST | `/api/auth/signup` | Create account |
  | POST | `/api/auth/login` | Login, returns JWT |
  | GET | `/api/auth/me` | Get current user |

  ### Flocks
  | Method | Route | Description |
  |--------|-------|-------------|
  | GET | `/api/flocks` | List user's flocks |
  | POST | `/api/flocks` | Create flock |
  | GET | `/api/flocks/:id` | Flock details |
  | PUT | `/api/flocks/:id` | Update flock |
  | DELETE | `/api/flocks/:id` | Delete flock |
  | POST | `/api/flocks/:id/join` | Accept invite |
  | POST | `/api/flocks/:id/invite` | Invite users |
  | POST | `/api/flocks/:id/decline` | Decline invite |
  | POST | `/api/flocks/:id/leave` | Leave flock |

  ### Budget Matching
  | Method | Route | Description |
  |--------|-------|-------------|
  | POST | `/api/budget/:flockId/submit` | Submit anonymous budget |
  | GET | `/api/budget/:flockId` | Get budget status (aggregate only) |
  | POST | `/api/budget/:flockId/lock` | Lock budget (creator only) |
  | POST | `/api/budget/:flockId/remind` | Remind non-submitters |

  ### Bill Splitting
  | Method | Route | Description |
  |--------|-------|-------------|
  | POST | `/api/billing/:flockId/create` | Create bill split |
  | GET | `/api/billing/:flockId` | Get bill details |
  | POST | `/api/billing/:flockId/settle` | Mark share as settled |
  | POST | `/api/billing/:flockId/ghost-commit` | Pre-commit to share |
  | GET | `/api/billing/:flockId/venmo-link` | Get Venmo deep-link |

  ### AI Assistant
  | Method | Route | Description |
  |--------|-------|-------------|
  | POST | `/api/ai/chat` | Send message to Birdie |

  ### AI Crowd Intelligence
  | Method | Route | Description |
  |--------|-------|-------------|
  | GET | `/api/crowd/:placeId` | Full venue prediction |
  | POST | `/api/crowd/batch` | Batch predictions |
  | GET | `/api/crowd/:placeId/alternatives` | Quieter alternatives |

  ### Messaging
  | Method | Route | Description |
  |--------|-------|-------------|
  | GET | `/api/flocks/:id/messages` | Flock messages |
  | POST | `/api/flocks/:id/messages` | Send message |
  | GET | `/api/dm` | All DM conversations |
  | GET | `/api/dm/:userId` | DMs with user |
  | POST | `/api/dm/:userId` | Send DM |

  ---

  ## Real-Time Events (Socket.io)

  - **Flock coordination:** `join_flock`, `leave_flock`, `send_message`, `typing`, `vote_venue`, `select_venue`, `update_location`
  - **AI agent:** `crowd_update`
  - **Budget:** `budget_updated`, `budget_locked`, `budget_reminder`
  - **Billing:** `bill_created`, `share_settled`, `bill_fully_settled`, `ghost_committed`
  - **Direct messages:** `dm_send_message`, `dm_typing`, `dm_react`, `dm_vote_venue`, `dm_share_location`, `dm_pin_venue`
  - **Social:** `flock_invite`, `friend_request`

